Leslie Fenton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leslie_Fenton 0 Leslie Fenton (12 March 1902 – 25 March 1978) was an English-born American actor and film director. He appeared in 62 films between 1923 and 1945. Leslie_Fenton ( 12_March_1902 – 25_March_1978 ) was an_English-born_American_actor_and_film_director . He appeared in 62_films between 1923_and_1945 .
